			<div class="has-no-title">
								<div class="slide-text"><p>Smarter. Better. Faster.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px;">Citadel trades across all major asset classes in the world’s largest markets. Our teams have a demonstrated track record of creating industry leading value &#8211; if you want to be exceptional, these are the people and tools you want to work with.</p>
</div>							</div>
