			<div class="slide-content">
			<div class="has-no-title">
								<div class="slide-text"><p>Big data drives big impact.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px;">Our Quantitative Strategies teams develop best of breed trading algorithms that drive real time, real world decisions. It’s one of the most compelling applications of big data in any industry.</p>
</div>							</div>
		</div>
	</div><div class="slide slide-3">

	<div class="slide-image">
