			<div class="slide-content">
			<div class="has-no-title">
								<div class="slide-text"><p>Write code that matters.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px;">Our software teams are helping write the future of finance. Leveraging our industry leading technology platform, and in partnership with some of the world’s brightest quantitative scientists and investment professionals, they drive our ability to win.</p>
