				<div class="text">
					<h2>Deepthi Shashidhar</h2>
					<h3>Software Engineer, Chicago</h3>
					<p>What’s it like to work at Citadel? Find out as global team members take a minute to give us a first person look inside.

For Deepthi, “#YearOne means being given responsibility that’s solely your own. It’s up to you to pursue greatness. It means seeing your work go into production – being able to see what you’ve created come to life.” </p>
				</div>
			</div>
