					<h2>Kim Jensen</h2>
					<h3>Quantitative Researcher, NY</h3>
					<p>What’s it like to work at Citadel? Find out as global team members take a minute to give us a first person look inside.

For Kim, “#YearOne means adding value to the company’s output immediately. It’s being able to have a conversation with some of the brightest minds in finance.”</p>
