<section class="row col2-right-layout col-645-315 sidebar-bkg-white container-campus-events">
			<article class="col-main content">
			<p style="font-family: arial; font-weight: bold; color: #00427a; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: -50px;">Upcoming Campus Events</p>
<p>We hold regular campus recruiting events for interested candidates. Please visit your university careers website for information regarding events and recruiting dates on you campus. If Citadel does not visit your campus, please send the following information to our Campus Recruiting team at <a href="mailto:campus.recruiting@citadel.com">campus.recruiting@citadel.com.</a></p>
<ul>
<li>Cover letter and resume (please be sure to include your cumulative and major GPA)</li>
<li>Standardized test scores (SAT/ACT or equivalent)</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="fulltime"></a></p>
