<p style="margin-top: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">Corporate Accounting</span></p>
<ul>
<li>Maintain and assist with various monthly reconciliations supporting general ledger activities</li>
<li>Compile monthly unaudited financial statements and annual audited financial statements</li>
<li>Assist with various monthly AP/AR entries</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">Internship opportunities available</span></p>
<p><a class="btn" href="mailto:campus.recruiting@citadel.com?subject=Finance and Accounting" rel="nofollow">Apply Now</a></p>
</div>
<div class="accordionButton" style="float: left; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; font-family: Georgia,serif; font-size: 18px; color: #51a5da; line-height: 23px; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 20px 0 10px 0; margin-top: 10px;">
<div class="button" style="float: left; border: 1px solid #51a5da; font-size: 34px; margin-top: 5px; padding: 2px 5px 7px; width: 22px; text-align: center;">+</div>
<div class="question" style="float: left; margin-left: 20px; width: 500px; color: #00427a; margin-top: 10px;">Treasury and Global Operations</div>
</div>
<div class="accordionContent" style="float: left; display: none; padding-left: 55px; padding-bottom: 15px;">
<p><strong>Operations Analyst Intern</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">If you aspire to:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>Work on a fast-paced, dynamic, and intellectually-challenging team</li>
<li>Collaborate internally and externally with trading/financing desks, counterparties, exchanges, prime brokers, and custodians</li>
<li>Add value by assisting in the lifecycle of a trade including clearance, settlements, and/or cash management</li>
<li>Add value by identifying and implementing technology and process-improvement opportunities, while demonstrating an intellectual curiosity and passion for innovation</li>
<li>Develop your skills and solve some of the most complex business problems in our industry</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">If you’ve got an interest in:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>Learning about financial markets and products</li>
<li>Working in a dynamic, fast-paced, and highly rewarding environment</li>
<li>Gaining exposure to best-in-class systems and processes</li>
<li>Understanding the full life-cycle of a trade from execution to clearance, settlement, and cash management</li>
<li>Learning about different types of securities financing, including prime brokerage, swap, tri-party, stock loan, and repo</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 20px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">If you’ve proven you have:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>A flexible but highly detail-oriented and results-driven approach to solving problems
<ul>
<li>Exceptional communication skills</li>
<li>A strong work ethic, intellectual curiosity &amp; high degree of integrity</li>
<li>Proficiency in Excel and data analysis. Familiarity with basic programming a plus.</li>
<li>An academic background and/or experience in an operational or quantitative field (engineering, accounting, finance, economics, math, or related disciplines)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>We are looking for candidates who are interested in a summer internship position. Part-time internship opportunity also available during the school year.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">Internship opportunities available</span></p>
<p><a class="btn" href="mailto:campus.recruiting@citadel.com?subject=Operations Analyst Intern" rel="nofollow">Apply Now</a></p>
</div>
<div class="accordionButton" style="float: left; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; font-family: Georgia,serif; font-size: 18px; color: #51a5da; line-height: 23px; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 20px 0 10px 0; margin-top: 10px;">
<div class="button" style="float: left; border: 1px solid #51a5da; font-size: 34px; margin-top: 5px; padding: 2px 5px 7px; width: 22px; text-align: center;">+</div>
<div class="question" style="float: left; margin-left: 20px; width: 500px; color: #00427a; margin-top: 10px;">Infrastructure</div>
</div>
<div class="accordionContent" style="float: left; display: none; padding-left: 55px; padding-bottom: 15px;">
<p><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">Information Security</span></p>
<ul>
<li>Knowledge of information security principles and practices to include, but not limited to, the following areas:
<ul>
<li>Vulnerability Scanning</li>
<li>Security Information and Event Management</li>
<li>Network Intrusion</li>
<li>Host Based Security (including mobile platforms)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Knowledge of network and system auditing and security assessment techniques is a plus</li>
<li>Good understanding of standard security/troubleshooting tools (Nessus, Nmap, tcpdump/WireShark, snort, burp, etc.)</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">Networking </span><br />
Experience with the following networking areas:</p>
<ul>
<li>LAN and WAN IP-based networking</li>
<li>Internet-facing network architectures</li>
<li>Wireless networking</li>
<li>Understanding of network protocols and communications (TCP/IP, multicast, unicast)</li>
<li>Network firewalls preferred</li>
<li>Network routing protocols (OSPF, BGP, etc) helpful</li>
<li>Cisco network hardware a plus</li>
<li>Any Cisco network certification is a plus</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-style: italic; text-transform: uppercase; color: #51a5da;">Internship opportunities available</span></p>
<p><a class="btn" href="mailto:campus.recruiting@citadel.com?subject=Infrastructure" rel="nofollow">Apply Now</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
